#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.translate:1
msgid "Map all characters in the string through the given mapping table."
msgstr "通过给定的映射表将字符串中的所有字符进行映射。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.translate:3
msgid "Equivalent to standard :meth:`str.translate`."
msgstr "等效于标准的 :meth:`str.translate`。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.translate
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.translate:5
msgid ""
"Table is a mapping of Unicode ordinals to Unicode ordinals, strings, or "
"None. Unmapped characters are left untouched. Characters mapped to None "
"are deleted. :meth:`str.maketrans` is a helper function for making "
"translation tables."
msgstr ""
"表是 Unicode 序数到 Unicode 序数、字符串或 None 的映射。未映射的字符保持"
"不变。映射为 None 的字符将被删除。:meth:`str.maketrans` 是用于创建转换表"
"的辅助函数。"

